{"tid":2100291,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全球確診逾千萬美突破3百萬　特朗普促學校秋天重開","createTime":"2020-07-09T03:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T03:08:49.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b572d6d37760ad8f26897624241f57653efec266","tid":2100291,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:06:35.000Z","msg":"全球確診逾千萬美突破3百萬 特朗普促學校秋天重開 <br />\n2020-07-09 HKT 06:02<br />\n<br />\n&quot;特朗普表示，德國、丹麥、挪威、瑞典及其他國家的學校已經重開，並沒有出現問題。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;(學校重開)對學童及家庭非常重要，(特朗普)又聲言，若學校在秋天不重開，聯邦撥款會被削減。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;秋天改為網絡授課的院校，所收外國留學生將不獲發簽證，哈佛大學和麻省理工學院已經入稟，尋求法院發出臨時禁制令，阻止美國政府執行這項命令。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536674-20200709.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536674-20200709.htm&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmuDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=03a1d89f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536674-20200709.htm&h=11999f6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536674-20200709.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">學業要緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e5f88a63b62183913ac0d9144b014fb662cb1fae","tid":2100291,"uid":278168,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:08:49.000Z","msg":"佢究竟想唔想連任"}]}